         <div type="translation" resp="part:vito">
             <p>Success! <foreign>Āyāga</foreign> panels were established as the pious gift — pertaining to the <foreign>dharmarājika</foreign> Adhālaka Shrine — of the renunciant Buddharakkhitā, pupil of master reverend Sa(ṃ)tika <supplied reason="lost">from Korugāla</supplied>.</p>
         </div>
